<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p>火山泡菜炒饭</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">1、1/4根京葱切细圈，半块午餐肉切丁，3片泡菜叶切丁备用。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200917/6673195e5d2c43b68a36f25bd5ded1dc.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">2、热锅冷油爆香京葱圈，下午餐肉丁先小火炒至表面焦黄。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200917/8d6ab02b1fee44108cfe55e2ebf94f36.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">3、再加泡菜丁和一大碗冷饭，转中火炒匀。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200917/af5befc978a54cc29f3143f468c92ec0.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">4、加1大勺泡菜汁、大半勺韩式辣酱、1勺辣椒粉和1勺生抽，翻炒均匀。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200917/4d5572ec9e834ad98a509dac4ff50dbc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">5、最后撒一把海苔碎，翻炒均匀。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200917/c867c298b2d44f17a4ccc6bf7e0a6350.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">6、将炒好的炒饭放入一个大圆碗中，压实，盖上小锅，连碗翻转倒扣在桌上，取走碗。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200917/3e64bfb705a34e6e9b7f6d5152fb312e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200917/9204fd2b238c49fdb5f137f4f55f4a41.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">7、炒饭中心借助筷子先戳出个洞，再整型出一条凹槽。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200917/a602781f634e426b87c6fcd1d2982b36.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">8、35g马苏里拉芝士入锅，最小火加热至融化。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200917/ed0503d20c494f3bae10410a329e719a.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">9、将芝士淋入炒饭中心。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200917/caa1192dcb6e4c1d8c1e8352bbb065d8.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">10、锅四周倒上少许油，将2颗鸡蛋打散后从炒饭顶部沿着凹槽浇在锅中。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200917/68960805dd9b4476b55cc575a5325ae0.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200917/ee967646a9b74a6e9bbf4d0c2b876ee8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">11、小火将蛋液煎熟，完成。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200917/2e507c664fd34e7aa1d9ec5e4a2971ae.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200917/6d7bde8740e540f58e4581a5d75554a0.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200917/0ffdfde1c6c74ffda6f55c76a380ab8b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200917/1037a1a2a3cd44a7bf471d22ff730a0a.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200917/620e92bbe9db4cf0af297134d8e3d19d.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200917/4cb2f29970d445e583594f76774de631.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">吃点幸福的食物，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">绽开孩子一样的笑容吧。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200917/442aaa927d984397b06fd608efe7b91f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>